{"tid":1691414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(回帶)  趙家賢:  緊急澄清, 無意叫義士送頭","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T00:39:28.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b50a0c24c7b1b2e817a8066447764e4761dd082d","tid":1691414,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"而家突然有人吹風向話民主黨趙家賢叫義士送頭, 比人咬係抵死<br />\n<br />\n推番呢段澄清先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/andrew.kychiu/posts/10157729080532189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fandrew.kychiu%2Fposts%2F10157729080532189&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axPGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=dc800e56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/andrew.kychiu/posts/10157729080532189</a><br />\n<br />\nAndrew Chiu 覺得火山爆發。<br />\n<br />\n#緊急澄清 剛才在太古站協助指引市民離開時，建議他們透過C出口(康怡)及E出口(太古城中心)離開。然而部分市民選擇了C出口上路面後，警方卻突然殺到無差別攻擊在場市民。蘋果更拍得警察在1米內近距離開槍，以及用警棍瘋狂攻擊在場市民。本人對此表示極度憤慨及遺憾。"},{"pid":"d752c3a3ee512732e758140948d0c289af835888","tid":1691414,"uid":297569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"希望大家嚟睇下 時刻保持冷靜同分析能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99309902ba49f7b233206eeecbe8fa6a19ae172e","tid":1691414,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d752c3a3ee512732e758140948d0c289af835888","tid":1691414,"uid":297569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"希望大家嚟睇下 時刻保持冷靜同分析能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"